{
  "texts": [
    "Researchers can rapidly adapt and release scalable generative and predictive biomolecular AI models built using NVIDIA cloud APIs.",
    "BioNeMo also allows the implementation of GAI in the generation of protein and biomolecule structure and function, which speeds up the development of novel molecules in the quest for drug discovery.",
    "The Pharma.",
    "AI platform has a total of three function-specific platforms: PandaOmics, Chemistry42, and inClinico.",
    "Through a patented network analysis system called iPanda that deduces pathway activation or inhibition, uncovering linkages between apparently distinct genes basis dysregulated biochemical processes, PandaOmics is developed to allow multi-omics identification of new targets."
  ]
}